Package Model.Menu

Enum Class Level

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Level>
Model.Menu.Level
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Level>, Constable
public enum Level extends Enum<Level>
Enumeration providing possible levels that can be reached by players, with descriptive and elegant names associated with each level.
